  openingSequence:
    enabled: 1
    lines:
    - Hi, you wayward soul! The kings three that judge the damned are currently indisposed
      so you will need to step in.
    - The job is simple. Sort the ouls based on the color of their sin. But dont
      forget to let the pure souls pass onto Elysium or lord Hades will be very mad.
    - Good luck!
  notifications:
  - triggerAtTime: 15
    message: Oh no! the souls are escaping their pits! Drag them back in!
